name: JASON LIVES (Aladinsane) By John Udbegrove
description: That Latex mask was sculpted by Jason Farrell and its called Aladinsane. This mask had been off the market for some time but the mold was sold to John Ubdegrove who is now offering them to the public. The mask fits heads 23.5 inches around, made with thick form fitting latex and it comes with resin teeth. John Ubdegrove is offering blanks as well as painted versions. Crystal Lake Industries is proud to now off this to you on our site. If you with to ask John questions about this mask please email crystallakeindustries@yahoo.com
